race.comment: DUNACH FIREBALL (1) boasts a strong record this course with nine wins and five minors from 26 tries. Was out of placings last time (27.92) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing fourth and beaten 2.25 lengths. With a clean break looks hard to beat. PAW ILLABO (4) finished well back at Sandown last time when a 5 length sixth (30.53) but scored four back at this track (27.56). Returns to favourable track. Can do much better this time. ONLY EASY (3) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at Shepparton, scoring by 1.3 lengths (25.41). Bold showing expected again. BRINDLE SURPRISE (6) will be thereabouts while fresh.
